==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oxhead
<hw>Ox"head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Hogshead</er>.]</ety> <def>Literally, the head of an ox (emblem of
cuckoldom); hence, a dolt; a blockhead.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Dost make a mummer of me, <qex>oxhead</qex>?</q>
<rj><qau>Marston.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oxheal</ent>⟦br⟧
